{"sections":{"ec32b834-e4e2-4e87-8392-6d45f7b82d33":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16177341137065__ec32b834-e4e2-4e87-8392-6d45f7b82d33-image-1":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_f9bb7d72-a950-4048-9149-0df0eddbde21.gif"}}},"block_order":["template--16177341137065__ec32b834-e4e2-4e87-8392-6d45f7b82d33-image-1"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":false,"remove_spacing_bottom":false,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"right","media_width":"7","content_position":"middleLeft","subheading":"<p><strong>LEARN WITH US<\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>Introducing, Yesterday, Today.<\/p>","description":"<p>Worlds collide in our exclusive new One-of-a-Kind collection: Yesterday, Today. <br\/><br\/>Evoking the best vintage design techniques, brought to life through our lens of conscious craftsmanship, these unique designs are conceived as true modern heirlooms.<br\/><br\/>Our first exclusive drop features 11 pieces inspired by vintage jewellery motifs, a mixture of One Of A Kind designs and limited-edition pieces, for this collection, we turned to vintage jewellery motifs; in particular the intricate, ornate features that shaped the 1700s-era Rococo movement.Using nature as a wellspring of inspiration, the period celebrated love, youth, drama and movement, manifested in curved, flowing lines and a luxurious brand of femininity. In approaching this new, exclusive collection, we drew upon the aesthetic imagination of the Rococo artisans and brought it to the present day, resulting in a harmony of modernity and classicism.<br\/><br\/><a href=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/collections\/yesterday-today\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/collections\/yesterday-today\"><strong>View The Collection<\/strong><\/a><\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"f2c7e461-17b5-4ac9-b3b5-cc2870417eb5":{"type":"off-grid","blocks":{"template--16105455616169__f2c7e461-17b5-4ac9-b3b5-cc2870417eb5-168013779007e0d978-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/6_ee714072-fdc8-45d7-9ee1-de3d11e9dead.png","link":""}},"0744ed6d-a384-4286-ba17-a4ad21dbf916":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_19ab6718-ddf5-410c-8295-e6234061e43b.png","link":""}},"08517d14-8851-463d-a56e-b36e7bdc6ff8":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Vintage_Frames_For_Web.gif","link":""}},"47d10691-87a6-4bb1-a95f-26c959aaec67":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7_3e5119ad-d0da-4c6f-ad91-553fc7ee9463.png","link":""}},"7da77d8a-d7f3-4b64-bf3e-f8747ee2dabf":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_87368f16-9b71-4170-a9c8-f769a8a96ff3.png","link":""}}},"block_order":["template--16105455616169__f2c7e461-17b5-4ac9-b3b5-cc2870417eb5-168013779007e0d978-0","0744ed6d-a384-4286-ba17-a4ad21dbf916","08517d14-8851-463d-a56e-b36e7bdc6ff8","47d10691-87a6-4bb1-a95f-26c959aaec67","7da77d8a-d7f3-4b64-bf3e-f8747ee2dabf"],"settings":{"enable_dark":false,"subheading":"","title":"","description":"<p>\"The inspiration for this collection focused around the use of motifs in vintage jewellery. We were particularly inspired by the ornate and intricate detailing as part of the Rococo movement of the 1700’s. Curving, flowing, curling lines, radiating femininity and luxury.Rococo arts are known for their depiction of love, youth, drama and movement with details often inspired by nature. We found the wildness and sentiment of this movement inspiring, and therefore built our collection around some of its many themes.\"<br\/><br\/>- Shona, Head Designer. <\/p>","feature_text":"<p>Heritage meets  <em><br\/>    contemporary craftsmanship. <\/em>One-of-a-kind <br\/>meets <em>everyday wear.<\/em><\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"fe4a59da